purpose: To provide a Rust SDK for privacy-preserving data analysis and processing using Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) techniques
principle: Leverages Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) to allow computations on encrypted data without decryption, ensuring data privacy
reusability: Offers a modular SDK with APIs for integrating FHE capabilities into Rust applications
limitations: Performance overhead due to encryption/decryption, limited to specific FHE schemes, requires understanding of cryptographic principles
name: mind-sdk-deepseek-rust
highlight: Enables privacy-preserving data processing using Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) in Rust
